    title RX FSM (recepção de protocolo) — switch-case
    [*] --> WAIT_STX
    WAIT_STX --> READ_LEN : byte == STX
    READ_LEN --> WAIT_STX : LEN == 0 / erro
    READ_LEN --> READ_DATA : LEN > 0
    READ_DATA --> READ_CHK : idx == LEN
    READ_CHK --> WAIT_ETX
    WAIT_ETX --> PROCESS : byte == ETX && checksum OK
    WAIT_ETX --> ERROR : byte != ETX || checksum NOK
    ERROR --> WAIT_STX
    PROCESS --> WAIT_STX
